snippet.title: I Made a Racing Game with No Experience
snippet.description:
Wishlist Apex Rush on Steam! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2638250/Apex_Rush/
I Made a Racing Game with No Experience in 1 week! This is one of my favorite projects I've done in a while! Starting the week knowing nothing about Unreal Engine 5 and how to make a game, to a working prototype with my own car model from Blender, handling, race track & more! 

I hope you all enjoy this video, and new concept for the channel, more to come this year. Drop a LIKE & Subscribe if you're new! 

My Clothing Brand: https://nosleep.co/
Discord: https://discord.gg/mCZ59bDsFr
